item.title: Prototype vs Infamous
item.dc:creator: @Young_Blitz Young Blitz
item.description:
@Young_Blitz wrote:

If you’re referring to the games of Prototype, then this is my perspective.
I downloaded Prototype on my PC with a torrent, and I use a ATI Radeon graphics card so it looks like I’m playing it on the actual system. The graphics look so realistic and the game is sick.

I play Assassins Creed on my PC now, so I don’t play Prototype most often now.
But, I would say Prototype is a beast.
